ng"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国 2 月份 CPI 同比连续第八个月下降，之后美联储有可能降息吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据新华财经消息，3 月 14 日晚，美国劳工部公布最新数据显示，2 月份美国 CPI 同比涨幅录得 6%，连续第八个月下降，也创 2021 年 9 月份以来最低值。环比涨幅为 0.4%，较 1 月份 0.5% 水平小幅回落。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7991b5c11bbbd4ed854fc2d508c7f890_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "100 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/589755293"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I88Hg+KyoquYHEAMaCDkzMzM4MzExIOmIxqAGMAA4PkAHcgk1ODk3NTUyOTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1679105039.3015969", "card_id": "Q_570019489", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 275}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "镇关西用荷叶包裹猪肉、晁盖用葫芦瓢喝酒、李逵蹲在地上赌钱，为什么《水浒传》的很多情景都如此富有美感？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在《水浒》中，类似的例子还有很多，例如林冲在山神庙喝酒吃牛肉、刘唐躺在灵官庙里睡觉、王婆坐在茶馆门前嗑瓜子、宋江在浔阳楼上喝酒题诗、张顺卖鱼、张横摆渡、武松夜走蜈蚣岭，所描述的事情都是平平无奇的，但会让读者感到一种惬意，一种美感。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a87ddc96d7699dbca02b82abbdc29788_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/570019489"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I88Hg+KyoquYHEAMaCDg4OTUzNTMxILn9opwGMCU4pAVACHIJNTcwMDE5NDg5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1679105039.3020914", "card_id": "Q_590115276", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "上汽大众补贴 37 亿跟进降价潮，单车最高优惠 5 万元，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "3 月 16 日晚，上汽大众